The programme is as under:-
a.
The programme shall be operational at all McDelivery 
                  
                  restaurants located in the cities of Mumbai and Navi 
                  
                  Mumbai and operated by HRPL.
b.
To participate in the programme, a customer has to call on McDelivery Number and has to purchase via McDelivery any food product at a regular menu price ("the order").
c.
In the programme buying/purchasing any food product at regular menu price means buying/purchasing, via McDelivery, any Burger, Fries, Drink, Dessert, Meal Combos (as listed on the Menu Board) (including Extra Value Meal ("EVM"), Family Meal, Happy Meal and Breakfast Meal) that HRPL offers.
d.
On purchase of any food product, via McDelivery, a customer shall get a free offer coupon ("offer coupon A") along with the order.
e.
Offer coupon A entitles a customer to get during the programme period, via McDelivery, a McChicken burger or a McVeggie burger absolutely free on his/her next purchase of an EVM via McDelivery.
                  
                  That means if a customer calls on McDelivery Number for the first time, he/she will get offer coupon A along with his/her order, which offer coupon A entitles him/her to get, via McDelivery, a McChicken or a McVeggie burger absolutely free on his/her next purchase, via McDelivery, of EVM and not otherwise. The customer will be entitled to get, subject to a maximum of four nos., one offer coupon A on every order placed by him/her via McDelivery.
f.
redeeming offer coupon A within 10 days from the date of issue of offer coupon A
                  
                  On the customer placing an order for the purchase of any food product, via McDelivery, for the fifth time during the
g.
programme period, he/she shall get a free coupon ("offer coupon B") along with the order.
                  
                  Offer coupon B entitles a customer to get, during the programme period, via McDelivery, a McChicken EVM - Medium or
h.
McVeggie EVM- Medium absolutely free on his/her next purchase of a Large Value Meal.
                  
                  That means if a customer calls on McDelivery Number for the fifth time, he/she will get offer coupon B along with his/her order, which offer coupon B entitles him/her to get a McChicken EVM - Medium or a McVeggie EVM - Medium absolutely free on his/her next purchase of Large Value Meal and not otherwise.
                  
