i.
edeeming offer coupon B within one (1) month from the date of issue of offer coupon B.
                  
                  On placing, during the programme period, the order for the fifth time via McDelivery, the customer is also entitled to
j.
receive, along with the order, a free gift hamper which shall consist of all the following items:
j.
