McVeggie EVM- Medium absolutely free on his/her next purchase of Large Value Meal via McDelivery.
                  
                  That means if the customer calls on McDelivery Number for the sixth time, he/she will get offer coupon B along with his/her order, which offer coupon B entitles him/her to get a McChicken EVM- Medium or a McVeggie EVM- Medium
m.
absolutely free on his/her next purchase of Large Value Meal and not otherwise. The customer will be entitled to get, subject to a maximum of four offer coupon B, one offer coupon on every order placed by him/her via McDelivery.
                  
